Package: bng-stack-runtime
Version: 1.0.1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Hendro Aritonang <hendroaritonang07@gmail.com>
Depends: vpp, vpp-plugin-core, vpp-plugin-dpdk, frr, python3
Recommends: accel-web-manager, vpp-snmp-agent
Description: BNG Stack Runtime — accel-pppd, VPP plugins, and system services
 Custom accel-pppd binary with VyOS VPP integration plugin (libvyos_vpp.so),
 PPPoE neighbor sync daemon, accel-ppp cleanup script, systemd service units,
 and VPP/sysctl configuration for a complete BNG stack deployment.
 .
 Assumes VPP custom build (vyos) is already installed.
Installed-Size: 1100
